Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report..._capture_paths(25.10)    timing_report..._capture_paths(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_pulse_width_matching_launch_capture_paths

Syntax
       timing_report_pulse_width_matching_launch_capture_paths {true | false}

       Default: false

       Reports pulse width paths that have matching launch and capture paths -
       the  count  of  pins and the pins must match exactly. The paths that do
       not meet this condition will not be reported.

       When set to true, the software will impact the minimum pulse width  re-
       port  that  is  generated with the report_min_pulse_width command along
       with the -path_type short and -path_type full_clock options.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

